{"tid":778961,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"趣趣地：范大將軍摑旁證被停職","createTime":"2018-08-14T05:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T05:38:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"327bee6cf98c5cc311333b8e6558a672543cf669","tid":778961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20180814/20475747\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475747&d=GoBdzZCraoQEJw9QjDPyFL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ba5bd13c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475747&h=8c1c0137\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20180814/20475747</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n趣趣地：范大將軍摑旁證被停職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/aa0104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Faa0104a.gif&h=856cee52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上海申花周日宣佈，暫停預備組教練范志毅嘅職務，據報呢位前中國國腳完場後因不滿判決出手摑旁證。申花指球隊作客上港嘅預備組比賽，教練范志毅作出「不理智行為」，球會決定暫停佢嘅職務。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/aa0104b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2Faa0104b.gif&h=0be3e9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然申花冇具體指佢做咗咩，不過內媒就登咗嗰場嘅賽後報告（圖），證實范志毅出手打人。報告指事發時已完場，范志毅就入場對球證嘅判決表達不滿，仲一手醒旁證一巴，禮拜一范志毅就公開道歉認錯。另一單中超笑料就係禮拜日長春對恒大，長春中場王壽挺昏迷送院，點知救護車尾門打唔開，搞成五分幾鐘先上到車，好彩最後冇事，不過足總就要求長春交代。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n拆局：新兵檢閱　基達搶晒鏡 (何西)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n趣趣地：C朗首戰入波好興奮"}]}